<p>In view</p>  <pre><code>@Html.EnumDropDownListFor(model =&gt; model.Field) </code></pre>  <p>Model</p>  <pre><code>public Fields Field { get; set; }  public enum Fields {     First = 1,     Second } </code></pre>  <p>These my markup</p>  <pre><code>&lt;select id="Field" name="Field"&gt;     &lt;option selected="selected" value="1"&gt; First&lt;/option&gt;     &lt;option value="2"&gt;Second&lt;/option&gt; &lt;/select&gt; </code></pre>  <p>These script dont call</p>  <pre><code>$('select#Field').change(function () {     var orderIdd = $('#Field').val();     alert(orderIdd); }); </code></pre>